I’ve identified a concrete miss: with a valid U.S.C. citation, heading text like “The administrative notice and hearing.” still yields zero formulas today. I’m now adding a deterministic relaxed heading fallback (for no-cue U.S.C. lines with leading stopwords) and regression tests for the three packet sample citations across parser, spaCy compiler, and modal compiler paths.
